## `test_fuse_access_syscall(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-fperm-8 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: syscall boundary; access() is its own FUSE callback -->

### Postconditions

```python
path = mount / "f"
path.write_bytes(b"x")

assert os.access(path, os.R_OK) is True
os.chmod(path, 0o000)
assert os.access(path, os.R_OK) is False
```

